{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/DataDrawing/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Eigenlicht","author":"Lilia Rusterholtz"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a0a1b728-2156-5787-b151-59579e0cd130","excerpt":"The Singapore-ETH Centre comprises research programs that address the challenges of modern societies worldwide, in urban environments and beyond. For the season…","html":"<p>The <a href=\"https://sec.ethz.ch/\">Singapore-ETH Centre</a> comprises research programs that address the challenges of modern societies worldwide, in urban environments and beyond.</p>\n<p>For the season’s greetings card, I created a visual concept that connects the scientific theme with the festive occasion: each country is represented by a snowflake. The resulting world map is a visualisation of UN-data, scraped from <a href=\"https://www.worldometers.info/world-population/population-by-country/\">Worldometers.</a> The population size corresponds to the size of the snowflake.</p>\n<div class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-nopointer\">\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/0399a/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 7vw 0; max-width: 2500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 48.160000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/529ab/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.webp 625w,\n/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/74e35/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.webp 1250w,\n/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/f3963/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.webp 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/0f1e4/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.jpg 625w,\n/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/597e0/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.jpg 1250w,\n/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/0399a/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.jpg 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/0399a/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Data drawing urbanisation different version\"\n          title=\"\"\n          src=\"/static/a8e5fc591196516d7d5b5aa4c75df8ed/0399a/DataDrawing_urbanisation_1.jpg\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</div>\n<p>Each year, different data is used: for the first edition, the hue is determined by the percentage of the urban population - the darker the color, the more urban the country.</p>\n<div class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-nopointer\">\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/0399a/DataDrawing_density.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 7vw 0; max-width: 2500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 48.160000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/529ab/DataDrawing_density.webp 625w,\n/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/74e35/DataDrawing_density.webp 1250w,\n/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/f3963/DataDrawing_density.webp 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/0f1e4/DataDrawing_density.jpg 625w,\n/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/597e0/DataDrawing_density.jpg 1250w,\n/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/0399a/DataDrawing_density.jpg 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/0399a/DataDrawing_density.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Data drawing world map density\"\n          title=\"\"\n          src=\"/static/13e3d4411e40af3f300715c347868953/0399a/DataDrawing_density.jpg\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</div>\n<p>For the second edition, hue reflects population density – the darker the color, the denser the country. The infographic is coded in <a href=\"https://d3js.org/\">D3</a>, with the kind help of Sergio Ordóñez for the snowflake logic.</p>\n<div class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-nopointer\">\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/0399a/DataDrawing_fertility.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 7vw 0; max-width: 2500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 48.160000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/529ab/DataDrawing_fertility.webp 625w,\n/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/74e35/DataDrawing_fertility.webp 1250w,\n/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/f3963/DataDrawing_fertility.webp 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/0f1e4/DataDrawing_fertility.jpg 625w,\n/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/597e0/DataDrawing_fertility.jpg 1250w,\n/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/0399a/DataDrawing_fertility.jpg 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/0399a/DataDrawing_fertility.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Data drawing world map fertility rate\"\n          title=\"\"\n          src=\"/static/234a2aa242a70897e3ad873b4e898482/0399a/DataDrawing_fertility.jpg\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</div>\n<p>Above is an example with hue reflecting fertility rate – with darker snowflakes representing more children. Using random parameters for the snowflakes, every single one is unique.</p>\n<p>Data stories are told in every individual version, but also in comparison within the series. Below is a version with hue reflecting aging societies, with darker snowflakes representing a higher percentage of people above 60. It is almost the exact opposite of the fertility rate version.</p>\n<div class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-width-full kg-nopointer\">\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/0399a/DataDrawing_over60.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin: 7vw 0; max-width: 2500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 48.160000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/529ab/DataDrawing_over60.webp 625w,\n/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/74e35/DataDrawing_over60.webp 1250w,\n/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/f3963/DataDrawing_over60.webp 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/0f1e4/DataDrawing_over60.jpg 625w,\n/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/597e0/DataDrawing_over60.jpg 1250w,\n/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/0399a/DataDrawing_over60.jpg 2500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n          src=\"/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/0399a/DataDrawing_over60.jpg\"\n          alt=\"Data drawing world map age above 60\"\n          title=\"\"\n          src=\"/static/6681a0daed4488e710a9f05c8c08c8a7/0399a/DataDrawing_over60.jpg\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n      </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Drawing with Data","date":"June 21, 2000","description":"Season's greetings card reflecting population size and density on a world map using unique snowflakes coded in Javascript.","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.414027149321267,"src":"/static/91dbb0d34e977b4fa08c58ff1bf6a3f0/ea7dd/DataDrawing_newsletter.jpg","srcSet":"/static/91dbb0d34e977b4fa08c58ff1bf6a3f0/53485/DataDrawing_newsletter.jpg 625w,\n/static/91dbb0d34e977b4fa08c58ff1bf6a3f0/f7dca/DataDrawing_newsletter.jpg 1250w,\n/static/91dbb0d34e977b4fa08c58ff1bf6a3f0/ea7dd/DataDrawing_newsletter.jpg 2500w,\n/static/91dbb0d34e977b4fa08c58ff1bf6a3f0/b85df/DataDrawing_newsletter.jpg 3500w","sizes":"(max-width: 2500px) 100vw, 2500px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/DataDrawing/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/SwissScales/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Swiss Scales Seoul"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}